{"title":"浪淘沙  读廖承志同志致蒋经国先生信","authors":["沈其震"],"dates":[{"year":1982,"month":8,"day":6}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"浪淘沙"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"读廖承志同志致蒋经国先生信"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沈其震"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如绘话家常，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"纸短情长，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生前身后妥商量。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一片至诚怀玉帛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"待束行装。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"兄弟愧阋墙，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"休再彷徨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"巧言令色刃如霜。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"计利幸求天下利，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"及早回航！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一九八二年七月"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}